data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This gorgeous home has a beautiful pool featuring a new liner and pump, an outdoor shower, a new roof in 2023 and a large covered patio area with 2 ceiling fans, as well as a beautifully landscaped yard. This place is perfect for relaxing and entertaining. A transfer switch for generator hookup is a great feature for any unexpected power outages. And let's not forget about the convenience of a large corner lot, a work shed, and a greenhouse with electricity. Inside, you'll find a cozy wood-burning fireplace and a spacious living area, It's like a little piece of paradise! No flood insurance is required and you’ll be close to schools and shopping. Don’t miss out on your chance to be in the middle of all the fantastic amenities Central has to offer!
